==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ingathering
<hw>In"gath`er*ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act or
business of gathering or collecting anything; especially, the gathering
of the fruits of the earth; harvest.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Thou shalt keep . . . the feast of <qex>ingathering</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Ex. xxii. 16.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ingelable</ent>⟦br⟧
